Has anyone seen this error from the IG Builder on an SD created by sushi?

Named items are out of order in the slice

I think it started after I updated the IG publisher (but can't be sure)...
and it's the latest version of sushi...
@David Hay -- I think we saw something like that once before, but neither we nor the reporter could reproduce it again. If you have a reproducible recipe, we'd love to take a look!
